{"tid":1611172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點建無人講今日中環活動","createTime":"2019-10-02T01:35:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T01:43:27.000Z","uid":273218,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"861e11f3e19e42238a7217da72594187d8cde60f","tid":1611172,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:35:59.000Z","msg":"我做過研究6月到依家<br />\n所有封站同放火都係股市收市時段進行<br />\n就連九巴報站都只會係831，或尋日呢d時候<br />\n說明因公眾活動暫定報站<br />\n今日正常報站即係睇死你地搞唔成<br />\n你話香港人因為要養家要返工出席唔到可以理解<br />\n但連對家都完全睇穿左股市開市時段無活動果下先離譜<br />\n點解大台唔吹風吹下有活動吹到好似尋日咁?<br />\n吹下風又無成本，需要既話大把網民配合宣傳<br />\n起碼比市民知道政府故意只選擇性周末封站<br />\n作為一個中環打工仔，我強烈希望今日下午可以被罷工"},{"pid":"170e1787d9ba8d1f84ea51853438816756b54df8","tid":1611172,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:37:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1610862/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1610862/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n今日12點半，黑西裝癱瘓全中環！！！！！！"},{"pid":"9b82400716c86615d266191c79fcaf4c0f3a948f","tid":1611172,"uid":160842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:38:02.000Z","msg":"今日12點半，黑西裝癱瘓全中環！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610862</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NKetoHi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNKetoHi.jpg&h=f1d047ba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aq4kZfD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAq4kZfD.jpg&h=a62839e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d65933a75fa8ad72cd5856abfe56a1d970d0d57c","tid":1611172,"uid":4363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:40:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f73039068d6959939fe6d695d44e76543ab6357","tid":1611172,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:41:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfa4f5cf0f4bb9f09e98110820d1f1feb13